sentences: Sterling Lauren Simms (born July 7, 1982), is an American R&B singer-songwriter.
His debut album, Yours, Mine & The Truth was released on December 23, 2008, by Def Jam Records.
In 2009, Sterling co-wrote "Robot Love," a song on Allison Iraheta's debut album "Just Like You," which will be released on December 1, 2009.
